member.summary:
this class supports connection to the Publishing Gateway server.
provides methods for:
 - connecting to Publishing Gateways and connection management;
- making interactive requests (via helper classes);
 - receiving asynchronous data and notifications;
 - validating and decoding asynchronous responses;
 The PublishingGatewayClient uses helper classes to implement interactive request functionality.
 PublishingGatewayClient is seldom used directly. Instead application programmers 
 usually derive their own class from PublishingGatewayClient and implement callback 
 interfaces to receive asynchronous notifications.
